# 🛠️ Technical Scenario Questions

---

# Q8️⃣ Why does website open slowly first time but faster second time?

### ✅ Strong Answer

Because of:

* browser caching
* DNS caching
* reused TCP connections

---

# Q9️⃣ Why is HTTPS important?

### ✅ Strong Answer

HTTPS encrypts communication using SSL/TLS to protect privacy and prevent attackers from reading data.

---

# Q🔟 What is CDN and why important?

### ✅ Strong Answer

CDN stores content closer to users, reducing latency and improving loading speed.

